The paper discusses logic-based executable agent specification languages for modeling and prototyping Multiagent Systems (MASs). This topic falls under the sub-fields of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Multiagent Systems (cs.MA), and Programming Languages (cs.PL). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
